<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <% include ../partials/head %>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="w3-container w3-blue">
    <h1>Survey of Innovation </h1>
  </div>
  <br>
  <br>
  <br>
  <br>
  <br>
  <br>
  <div class="w3-row">
    <div class="w3-col" style="width: 10%;"><p> </p></div>
    
    <div class="w3-col w3-row" style="width: 80%">

      <div class="w3-border-bottom w3-row">
        <div class="w3-col w3-twothird">
          <label class="w3-xlarge">1. Do you like Innovation?</label>
        </div>

        <div class="w3-col w3-third"> 
          <label>
            <input class="w3-radio w3-border" type="radio" name="q1" value="yes">
          Yes
          </label>
          &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;
          <label>
            <input class="w3-radio w3-border" type="radio" name="q1" value="no">
          No
          </label> 
        </div>
                   
      </div>
      <br>

      <div class="w3-border-bottom w3-row">
        <div class="w3-col w3-twothird">
          <label class="w3-xlarge">2. Have you participated in any Innovation activities? </label>
        </div>

        <div class="w3-col w3-third"> 
          <label>
            <input class="w3-radio w3-border" type="radio" name="q2" value="yes">
          Yes
          </label>
          &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;
          <label>
            <input class="w3-radio w3-border" type="radio" name="q2" value="no">
          No
          </label> 
        </div>
                   
      </div>
      <br>

      <div class="w3-border-bottom w3-row">
        <div class="w3-col w3-twothird">
          <label class="w3-xlarge"> 3. Which activities you like most? </label>
        </div>

        <div class="w3-col w3-third"> 
          <select class="w3-select" name="q3">
            <option value="Innovation Hour">Innovation Hour</option>
            <option value="Inno-Storm">Inno-Storm</option>
            <option value="Bike-Grapher">Bike-Grapher</option>
            <option value="BLateral Thinking Workshop">Lateral Thinking Workshop</option>            
          </select>        
        </div>
        <br> 
        <br>
      </div>
      <div class="w3-border-bottom w3-row">
        <div class="w3-col w3-twothird">
          <label class="w3-xlarge">4. In your point of view, is Innovation Hour helpful for you? If no, please let us know which points should be improved? </label>
        </div>

        <div class="w3-col w3-third"> 
          <label>
            <input class="w3-radio w3-border" type="radio" name="q4" value="yes">
          Yes
          </label>
          &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;
          <label>
            <input class="w3-radio w3-border" type="radio" name="q4" value="no">
          No
          </label> 
        </div>
                   
      </div>
      <br>

      <div class="w3-border-bottom w3-row">
        <div class="w3-col w3-twothird">
          <label class="w3-xlarge">5. In general, which is your expectation from Innovation Champion to support you in Innovation activities? </label>
        </div>

        <div class="w3-col w3-third"> 
            <textarea placeholder="Type here..." rows="5"  cols="20" name="q5">

            </textarea>
        </div>
                   
      </div>
      <br>
      <br>      
    </div>

    <div class="w3-col" style="width: 10%;"> <p> </p></div>
  </div>
  <br>
  <br>
  <br>
  <br>
  <br>
  <br>
  <div class="w3-container w3-blue">
    <p> Innovation Champions </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
